---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const EMAIL = 'hello@enablement.engineering';
const LINKEDIN = 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/enablement-engineering/';
---

<Layout title="Contact | Enablement Engineering" description="Get in touch to discuss how we can help enable your team's capabilities">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-ink leading-tight">
					Start the Conversation
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
					Ready to build capabilities that enable your team to achieve more? Let's discuss your goals and explore how we can help.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Contact Content -->
		<section class="py-16">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
				<!-- Get In Touch -->
				<div class="space-y-8">
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-ink">Get In Touch</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
							Whether you have a specific challenge in mind or want to explore possibilities, I'd love to hear from you.
						</p>
					</div>

					<a
						href={`mailto:${EMAIL}`}
						class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-accent focus-visible:ring-offset-2 bg-accent-500 text-secondary-900 hover:bg-accent-600 h-14 px-10"
					>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
						</svg>
						{EMAIL}
					</a>

					<p class="text-neutral-500">
						Or connect on{' '}
						<a href={LINKEDIN} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link-600 hover:text-link-700 underline underline-offset-4">
							LinkedIn
						</a>
						<span class="block text-sm mt-2">I typically respond within 24 hours.</span>
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- What to Expect -->
				<div class="card-base p-8 off-kilter-0-5">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-6">What to Expect</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-4 text-neutral-600">
						<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
							<span>Initial conversation to understand your needs</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
							<span>Collaborative scoping and proposal development</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
							<span>Transparent timeline and milestone planning</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
							<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
							<span>Ongoing communication throughout the engagement</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- FAQ Section -->
		<section class="py-16 bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl off-kilter-0-5">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
				<div class="text-center space-y-6">
					<h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">What happens when the AI gets something wrong?</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">It will. That's why we build glass box systems—when something fails, you can see exactly what happened and why. For compliance work, "the AI made a mistake" isn't an acceptable answer. "Here's the decision trace, here's where the logic broke down, here's how we've updated the procedure" is.</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Will I need you forever?</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">No, and that's the point. Our goal is your independence. We build systems you can audit, modify, and extend without us. We document everything, train your team, and design for handoff from day one. Some clients keep us around for new initiatives. Others run everything themselves. Both are success cases.</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Where does my data go?</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Nowhere you don't control. Your data stays in your infrastructure. We don't require data to leave your environment, we don't train models on your information, and we build systems that work with your data governance requirements, not around them.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">How is this different from typical AI consulting?</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Most AI work optimizes for automation or engagement. We optimize for capability extension—making people more effective while keeping them in control. We build procedures that produce evidence, not just outputs. Systems where reasoning is visible. Skills that transfer across platforms rather than locking you in.</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Can you work with our existing systems?</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Yes, and we prefer to. We're not here to sell you a platform. We build on what you have, integrate with your existing tools, and design procedures that aren't locked to any single vendor—including us. The skills we create are portable, documented, and yours to keep.</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">How long does an engagement take?</h3>
							<p class="text-neutral-600">Depends on scope, but we structure everything around early value and clear milestones. A focused initiative might be 6-8 weeks. A larger transformation might be 6 months. Either way, we're optimizing for getting you to independence, not billable hours.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
</Layout>
